    %section
        %h2.s4 How it all comes together
        %p At the beginning of each new product launch, we have a multidisciplinary kickoff with product, design, copy, and marketing. Together, we decide the sandwich’s high-level components based on the product’s features, importance, and marketing strategy. Then the designer and copywriter pair to create the page.
