    %section.summary
        %p.large The PDP sandwich template is now fully developed, integrated into our CMS, and rolled out to all product pages. Because of this, we can now launch product pages 80% faster! The consistent template also allows us to rapidly A/B test improvements to the pages. One such optimization &mdash; moving the product discovery section higher up on the PDPs &mdash; has had a $5,760,000 increase in yearly revenue alone. We’ve also increased one of our most important PDP’s conversion rate by 28.75% and subsequent revenue on that page by 33.22% YOY.

